        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Rural Transportation Equity Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill establishes within the Department of Transportation (DOT) the Office of Rural Investment to ensure that rural transportation needs are addressed and prioritized in DOT policies, programs, and activities. The bill also establishes a rural transportation advisory council to consult with and advise the office.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
